flowchart LR
    GH[GitHub Repository] --> CI[GitHub Actions / GHCR]
    CI --> WEB[Next.js Web + Telegram Mini App on Vercel]
    CI --> CP[Ubuntu Control Plane]
    CP --> API[NestJS Business API]
    CP --> RW[Remnawave]
    CP --> DB[(PostgreSQL)]
    CP --> REDIS[(Redis)]
    API --> BOT[Telegram Bot]
    WEB --> API
    API --> RW
    RW --> N1[VPN Node 1]
    RW --> N2[VPN Node 2]
    N1 --> X1[Xray: VLESS + REALITY + Vision]
    N2 --> X2[Xray: VLESS + REALITY + Vision]
    N1 --> H1[Hysteria 2 fallback]
    N2 --> H2[Hysteria 2 fallback]
    N1 --> A1[AmneziaWG optional]
    N2 --> A2[AmneziaWG optional]
    MON[Prometheus + Grafana + Loki] --> CP
    MON --> N1
    MON --> N2
    BACKUP[Encrypted Backup + Restore Test] --> DB
    INSTALL[PowerShell + Ubuntu One-click Installer] --> CP
    INSTALL --> N1
    INSTALL --> N2
    HF[Hugging Face optional anonymized analytics] -. aggregated metrics only .-> MON
